{"tid":758961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[走數]支那男遇溺西貢浪茄灣送院不治","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:16:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T08:30:36.000Z","uid":51271,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f4318a367eab38be227bd8499353834bd09f6f42","tid":758961,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:16:40.000Z","msg":"一名內地男子在西貢浪茄灣遇溺，直升機送院搶救後，證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n事發在中午12時許，58歲男事主由他妻子救起時已經昏迷，並由他們的女兒報警。警方相信事件沒有可疑。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409381-20180728.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409381-20180728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Qs%2FWYXSXxEG7f5jIpYGn3r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=9bb5d3b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409381-20180728.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d66f1005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409381-20180728.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"509a691f326421b8cf96732352f9b979b855a12f","tid":758961,"uid":53466,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"923bc38752dafcf7927b19924f284bd7c0f0e7ee","tid":758961,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:33:46.000Z","msg":"又被溺斃啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f709548696d8165139e963a8c18fcc2bd605547c","tid":758961,"uid":136662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"要告泳灘無人當面警告佢地有危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adbccc2ccf564a7fa26cb3734124914f8527fd3","tid":758961,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a75b0b3781a4397fce7ed9c83c8f8559741c1e","tid":758961,"uid":188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"有無追討返佢隻屋企人救援費用?"},{"pid":"8cde20a58c62e052f318042982f1cc9bc04dbaaa","tid":758961,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"浪茄一向有暗湧<br />\n自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d419f3aba93fdae023f921bef3d53854a6f12f6c","tid":758961,"uid":36551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:46:05.000Z","msg":"係咪個沙灘太少人，游唔慣呀？<br />\n平時支那啲泳池沙灘人貼人咁游，點會遇溺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20150712/large/1436707866_944f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20150712%2Flarge%2F1436707866_944f.png&h=a1c9e2a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af31fdb6b6fcceeb6ef5762c4f0b9696a679429a","tid":758961,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:46:26.000Z","msg":"由得佢浮返支那咪算囉"},{"pid":"436bbea40587b66a433788566a5ed8765bb43b65","tid":758961,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"高危大浪西灣秋季藏殺機<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今次發生遇溺失蹤意外的大浪西灣，是西貢五大危險海灘之一，過往曾發生遇溺事件，據熟悉現場環境的專家稱，每逢秋初轉季候風，大浪西灣暗湧大，非常危險，絕不宜游泳，否則隨時「搵命較飛」。<br />\n東北風一起 波濤洶湧<br />\n西貢五大危險泳灘，分別是大蛇灣、鹹田灣、浪茄灣、甕缸灣及大浪西灣。記者昨租船出海採訪搜救時，由於受到颱風凱薩娜及東北季候風影響，海面風勢漸大，白浪翻天，船隻顛簸不堪，海浪拍打上船，記者亦全身濕透。船家指出，東北風一起，大浪西灣必定波濤洶湧，即使大船駛過也難免搖晃不定。<br />\n<br />\n曾多次在大浪西灣潛水的浸會大學體育系副教授雷雄德稱，夏天吹西南風時，大浪西灣水平如鏡，適合潛水活動，但踏入秋季，季候風轉變，該處浪急暗湧大，海底礁石眾多，非常危險，所以不適合玩水上活動。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，每次發生溺斃慘劇，離不開兩大原因，一是當事人對所玩的活動認識不足，警覺性低；二是遇事時驚慌過度，不懂自救。他提醒參與水上活動人士，欺山莫欺水。"},{"pid":"bdc77923bf53afc66d4aa8c739acf1dc506ecadf","tid":758961,"uid":14244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"浪費人力物力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44de438b3a7d056be74d16c8e3ef6f17d168021","tid":758961,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d87cd38652958e22f28ad061153ac2909922ecd","tid":758961,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b9c9ec1a92c226f2e2bcc29ae7dd2b1c53678a7","tid":758961,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"打針未呀五毛"},{"pid":"e63a3be803fa0242dfe27ece9e18ee46724e24af","tid":758961,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2132df39550238b6aeddeaf9706e0a091739cd","tid":758961,"uid":117237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d87cd38652958e22f28ad061153ac2909922ecd","tid":758961,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bdc77923bf53afc66d4aa8c739acf1dc506ecadf","tid":758961,"uid":14244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"浪費人力物力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T08:30:36.000Z","msg":"佢浪費係一件事<br />\n<br />\n呢件支那狗就一定浪撚費<br />\n佢有冇撚交稅<br />\n<br />\n報警叫飛機黎有冇找數<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦<br />\n想轉移視線<br />\n比多少少力"}]}